29:04.642 --> 29:07.385
I know he wasn't much of a father,

29:08.012 --> 29:11.085
but he was a hell of a man.

29:45.750 --> 29:47.284
How's it goin', Mango?

29:47.285 --> 29:49.352
Hey, Twinkle Toes Cantara.

29:49.353 --> 29:52.021
