30:49.614 --> 30:52.182
<i>ETA approximately five hours.</i>

30:52.183 --> 30:55.018
<i>Copy that, Viper-One.
Be safe out there.</i>

31:46.203 --> 31:47.871
<i>This is Tiger-Two Seven to Tower.</i>

31:47.872 --> 31:50.473
<i>We're ready and awaitin'
your command, over.</i>

31:50.474 --> 31:51.975
<i>This is Tower.</i>

31:51.976 --> 31:53.176
<i>You're cleared for take-off.</i>

31:53.177 --> 31:56.489
<i>Confirm Team Viper's on
board, ready for incursion.</i>

31:57.548 --> 32:01.088
<i>That's affirmative,
the team's locked and loaded.</i>

32:04.088 --> 32:07.223
<i>We are approximately 80
minutes from DZ Alpha Bravo.</i>

32:07.224 --> 32:10.104
<i>Roger that, Tiger-Two
Seven, be safe out there.</i>

33:32.977 --> 33:34.577
- Major Shope!
- Bidwell?

33:34.578 --> 33:36.312
Yeah.

33:36.313 --> 33:37.947
They call you Bullet-Face, right?

33:37.948 --> 33:40.150
I have heard that before, yes.

33:40.151 --> 33:43.395
This is Sanaa Malik, Eddie Cantara.

33:43.521 --> 33:44.921
Sniper?

33:44.922 --> 33:46.289
I prefer the word shooter.

33:46.290 --> 33:47.690
Okay.

33:47.691 --> 33:49.659
Now we know who we all are.

33:49.660 --> 33:52.629
Sol heard somebody wants me dead?

33:52.630 --> 33:54.864
Well, tell 'em to take a number.

33:54.865 --> 33:58.768
Everybody within a thousand
klicks of here wants me dead.

33:58.769 --> 34:02.505
Someone in particular, linked to
what you were doing in Afghanistan

34:02.506 --> 34:04.808
on April the 22nd, 2004.

34:04.809 --> 34:08.178
Yes, Sentinel.
I remember that mission.

34:08.179 --> 34:09.379
Afghanistan.

34:09.380 --> 34:12.382
We were escorting a group
of Army Intel out of theater.

34:12.382 --> 34:13.683
We were ambushed.

34:13.684 --> 34:18.487
It was a cluster fuck. We lost
half the men to friendly fire.

34:18.489 --> 34:21.630
Someone is killing every officer
who served on that mission.

34:23.393 --> 34:25.431
You're the last one alive.

35:01.398 --> 35:04.434
380 tons of heroin and
morphine is produced

35:04.435 --> 35:07.537
in Afghanistan and
trafficked up into Europe.

35:07.538 --> 35:10.540
The Heroin Highway starts
in the Helmand River Valley

35:10.541 --> 35:16.279
and moves through Iran, Iraq and
then into Syria before entering Turkey

35:16.280 --> 35:18.748
and making its way into Europe.

35:18.749 --> 35:22.218
These drugs bankroll terrorism
and it's our job to stop it.

35:22.219 --> 35:23.786
They move through small villages,

35:23.787 --> 35:27.725
sometimes forcing the local men
and women to work as slave labor.

35:30.861 --> 35:34.197
<i>These cartels are
protected by kill squads.</i>

35:34.198 --> 35:36.499
<i>At 1800 today, the group
we've been hunting</i>

35:36.500 --> 35:39.702
will deliver the heroin to a
town on the outskirts of Bayda

35:39.703 --> 35:42.539
in exchange for weapons.

35:42.540 --> 35:44.107
<i>My team's forward deployed.</i>

35:44.108 --> 35:46.543
<i>They're getting in position now.</i>

35:46.544 --> 35:50.013
We will be there to say
hello and fuck them up.

35:50.014 --> 35:52.115
In and out in 30 minutes.

35:52.116 --> 35:55.051
<i>This is an urban op, ladies.</i>

35:55.052 --> 35:58.187
I don't need to remind you
there's an 88% casualty rate.

35:58.188 --> 35:59.756
Don't silhouette, watch your angles

35:59.757 --> 36:01.724
and stay out of the fatal funnel.

36:01.725 --> 36:05.061
<i>The drugs and weapons
will be destroyed on site.</i>

36:05.062 --> 36:07.839
This is not a recovery mission.

36:07.865 --> 36:10.400
We leave zero signature.

36:10.401 --> 36:12.371
Questions?

36:20.277 --> 36:22.212
Thank you.

36:22.913 --> 36:24.447
Right.

36:24.448 --> 36:29.285
While Major Shope and your I.N.L.
team are busy fucking them up,

36:29.286 --> 36:33.089
my boys and girls will be on the
green-side providing long-range support.

36:33.090 --> 36:35.291
For those of you who skipped class,

36:35.292 --> 36:37.727
that's short for
sniping in the weeds.

36:37.728 --> 36:39.698
Thank you.

36:40.230 --> 36:44.567
We'll also be filling the surrounding
areas with these little babies.

36:44.568 --> 36:46.836
GSM surveillance devices,

36:46.837 --> 36:52.108
<i>real time HD audio and video
with an IR range of 60 feet.</i>

36:52.109 --> 36:55.445
<i>I'll be monitoring all the video
feeds on the crisis zone.</i>

36:55.446 --> 37:00.176
<i>If it moves with a gun,
we will watch it in HD.</i>

37:00.984 --> 37:05.822
Whoever shows up to
kill you is the bad guy.

37:05.823 --> 37:08.925
We've invited him with a stream
of unsecured radio chatter

37:08.926 --> 37:12.402
pinpointing the town and
your team's presence there.

37:14.765 --> 37:17.366
So, if this guy shows
you've got my back?

37:17.367 --> 37:18.301
We have.

37:18.302 --> 37:21.307
You any good with those
long-guns, Major?

37:21.705 --> 37:25.779
I'd rather take my long-guns,
than your short arms.

37:27.144 --> 37:29.079
Well said.

37:29.847 --> 37:31.919
Gear up.

37:33.283 --> 37:35.253
Let's get it done.

37:54.371 --> 37:56.973
YOUR PAPERS? IDENTIFICATION.

37:56.974 --> 37:59.409
I'm just passing through.
I don't want any trouble.

37:59.410 --> 38:01.380
PUT YOUR HANDS UP!

38:03.981 --> 38:07.293
Come on, guys. Let's not do this.

38:41.018 --> 38:42.785
- Here it is.
- Good.

38:42.786 --> 38:45.666
800 meters out from
the center of town.

38:53.597 --> 38:57.706
Sir, if I may, why do they
call you Bullet-Face?

38:59.603 --> 39:02.605
I've had 74 confirmed kills.

39:02.606 --> 39:07.181
And 67 of those have
been face shots.

39:07.277 --> 39:10.214
- Quite a statement.
- More of a trademark.

39:11.648 --> 39:15.118
Sir, why did you leave
Brandon behind?

39:15.119 --> 39:18.693
There's more at play here
than you need to know about.

39:18.722 --> 39:22.796
But I do what's right in
the moment at the time.

39:23.127 --> 39:26.200
- You always know what's right for us?
- Yeah, pretty much.

39:26.797 --> 39:28.869
You think you could ever be wrong?

39:30.334 --> 39:32.508
Keeps me awake at night.

39:35.105 --> 39:38.178
Okay, get ghillied-up, play hide.

40:24.388 --> 40:27.957
Lots of friendlies out
there, no tangos.

40:27.958 --> 40:30.030
Roger that.

41:10.701 --> 41:14.904
Viper-Two, Viper-Two,
this is Viper-One, over.

41:14.905 --> 41:19.508
