42:54.304 --> 42:56.872
Any sign of Tango, over?

42:56.873 --> 42:58.708
Negative, over.

42:58.709 --> 43:00.543
Keep your eyes on the prize.

43:00.544 --> 43:02.878
Find me Simpson. Viper-One, out.

43:02.879 --> 43:05.087
Roger that.

43:13.623 --> 43:17.693
Major, how's everything
going out there?

43:17.694 --> 43:19.228
This shithead pushing
up daisies yet?

43:19.229 --> 43:21.163
I'm in the middle of it now.

43:21.164 --> 43:22.631
Gunnery Sergeant Beckett with you?

43:22.632 --> 43:24.333
He's confined to base.

43:24.334 --> 43:25.501
Is he?

43:25.502 --> 43:27.136
<i>That's where I left him.</i>

43:27.137 --> 43:30.643
Well, he's gone. Hasn't
been seen since yesterday.

43:32.009 --> 43:33.979
That's news to me.

43:34.211 --> 43:37.146
I'm starting to get a bad
feeling about this, Major.

43:37.147 --> 43:38.247
Finish it!

43:38.248 --> 43:41.817
So no pressure then. Just hurry up.

43:41.818 --> 43:44.163
Exactly, Major.

43:44.321 --> 43:45.921
No more Marines dying.

43:45.922 --> 43:47.994
Roger that.

43:57.567 --> 44:01.471
Okay, boys. Stay sharp now.

44:11.348 --> 44:14.950
Viper-One, Viper-One, got a
second truck at my 10 o'clock.

44:14.951 --> 44:17.296
Roger that, Viper-Two.

44:30.767 --> 44:35.444
Team Alpha, Team Bravo,
get ready to bound.

44:47.818 --> 44:49.788
Let's go.

45:00.397 --> 45:01.764
Team Charlie, you are on me.

45:01.765 --> 45:04.008
We're fire support.

45:04.968 --> 45:07.211
Take that window.

45:07.471 --> 45:09.475
You take that window.

45:45.075 --> 45:47.109
Shit. We're made.

45:47.110 --> 45:49.045
Shooter!

45:49.312 --> 45:51.413
Take them! Take them now!

46:12.869 --> 46:14.907
Which way? Which way?

46:30.987 --> 46:32.121
Should we engage?

46:32.122 --> 46:34.557
Protect Shope and look for
Tango. That's our mission.

46:34.558 --> 46:37.199
<i>Keep your head down on that scope.</i>

46:37.827 --> 46:41.765
Advance, advance! Move in!
Cover me! Cover me!

47:25.242 --> 47:28.918
Viper-Two, Viper-Two,
we've got enemy sniper fire.

47:35.118 --> 47:37.759
ATB Tangos, 11 o'clock.

47:39.856 --> 47:41.290
Fuck!

47:41.291 --> 47:44.467
Cantara? Cantara?

47:49.599 --> 47:52.568
Viper-One, Viper-One, this is
Viper-Two. I got a man down!

47:52.569 --> 47:55.537
They've got counter-sniper
support. How copy?

47:55.538 --> 47:57.473
Start shooting.

48:26.936 --> 48:28.270
We're pinned!

48:28.271 --> 48:31.344
We need to change this fucking game!

48:33.743 --> 48:35.678
Gotcha, bitch.

49:11.481 --> 49:13.649
Nice work. That's a game changer.

49:13.650 --> 49:15.756
